msgstr "Rezime tab je vertikalno podijeljen u dvije polovine."

#. Tag: title
#: details-forecast.docbook:260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Summary"
msgstr "Rezime računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left is the Account Summary, displaying one row of information for "
"each Asset and Liability, with the columns shows below. Note that if the "
"Forecast is based on Scheduled and Future Transactions, there will only be "
"rows for accounts referenced in such transactions."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:270 details-forecast.docbook:361
#: details-forecast.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account"
msgstr "Račun"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:272 details-forecast.docbook:363
#: details-forecast.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid "The name of the Asset or Liability account"
msgstr "Ime Asset ili Liability računa"

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:277
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:279
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "The current balance of the account is displayed."
msgid "The current balance of the account"
msgstr "Trenutni bilans računa je prikazan."

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Account Cycle Balance"
msgstr "Bilans ciklusa računa"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Forecast period is split into account cycles. The default account cycle "
"length is 30 days, but can be set by the user."
msgstr ""
"Period prognoze je podijeljen u cikluse računa. Po definiciji, ciklus računa "
"je 30 dana, ali to korisnik može promijeniti."

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:291
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The first account cycle date is the first Forecast date. By default this "
#| "is the current date plus one account cycle, but can change depending on "
#| "the \"Day of Month to start Forecast\" setting."
msgid ""
"The first account cycle date is the first Forecast date. By default this is "
"the current date plus one account cycle, but this can change depending on "
"the \"Day of Month to start Forecast\" setting."
msgstr ""
"Prvi datum ciklusa računa je prvi datum prognoze. Po definiciji to je "
"treutni datum plus jedan ciklus računa, ali može biti promijenjen u "
"ovisnosti o \"Day of Month to start Forecast\"(dan u mjesecu za početak "
"prognoze) postavci."

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:297
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Remaining account cycle dates are determined by adding the account cycle "
#| "length to the previous account cycle date. This is continued until the "
#| "calculated account cycle date would be beyond the Forecast period."
msgid ""
"The remaining account cycle dates are determined by adding the account cycle "
"length to the previous account cycle date. This is continued until the "
"calculated account cycle date would be beyond the Forecast period,or Days to "
"Forecast."
msgstr ""
"Preostali datumi ciklusa računa se računaju dodavanjem dužine ciklusa računa "
"na prethodni datum ciklusa računa. Tako se računaju sve dok sljedeći datum "
"ciklusa računa ne bude prelazio period prognoze."

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "For each account cycle date the predicted balance is displayed."
msgstr "Za svaki datum ciklusa računa, pretpostavljeni bilans je prikazan."

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:308 details-forecast.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "Total Variation"
msgstr "Ukupna varijacija"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:310 details-forecast.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rightmost column displays the predicted difference in value between the "
"balances at the start and end of the forecast. If the predicted end value of "
"the account (in terms of net worth) is less than the start value the whole "
"row is highlighted in red."
msgstr ""
"Krajnja desna kolona prikazuje pretpostavljenu razliku u vrijednosti između "
"bilansa na početku i na kraju prognoze. Ukoliko je krajnja prepostavljena "
"vrijednost računa(posmatrajući neto iznos) manja od početne vrijednosti, "
"cijela kolona će biti istaknuta crvenom bojom."

#. Tag: title
#: details-forecast.docbook:321
#, no-c-format
msgid "Key Summary Information"
msgstr "Ključne informacije rezimea"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:322
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The bottom half of the Summary tab displays noteworthy information about "
#| "accounts. This includes:"
msgid ""
"The right portion of the Summary tab displays noteworthy information about "
"accounts. This includes:"
msgstr ""
"Dionja polovina rezime taba prikazuje važne informacije o računu. One "
"uključuju:"

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assets below zero"
msgstr "Asset račune ispod nule"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:331
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A message is displayed for any asset for which the value starts or will "
#| "drop below zero during the forecast period."
msgid ""
"A message is displayed (in red) for any asset account for which the value "
"starts or will drop below zero during the forecast period."
msgstr ""
"Poruka je prikazana za sve Asset račune za koje vrijednost počinje ili će "
"pasti ispod nule tokom perioda prognoze."

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Liabilities above zero"
msgstr "Liabilitiy računi iznad nule"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:341
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A message is displayed for any liability for which the value starts or "
#| "will rise above zero during the forecast period. Note that the value of a "
#| "liability is the negative of its ledger balance, since a positive balance "
#| "indicates money owed."
msgid ""
"A message is displayed for any liability account for which the value starts "
"or will rise above zero during the forecast period. Note that the value of a "
"liability is the negative of its ledger balance, since a positive balance "
"indicates money owed."
msgstr ""
"Poruka je prikazana za sve Liability račune za koje vrijednost počinje ili "
"će porasti iznad nule tokom perioda prognoze. Primijetite da je vrijednost "
"Liability računa suprotna od one prikazane u tabeli, pošto pozitivna "
"vrijednost ukazuje novac koji dugujete."

#. Tag: title
#: details-forecast.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Details Tab"
msgstr "Tab detalji"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Details tab also displays one row for each Asset and Liability account, "
"but the columns displayed differ from the Summary Tab."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: details-forecast.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Dates"
msgstr "Datumi"

#. Tag: para
#: details-forecast.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each date in the Forecast period a column displays the predicted balance "
"of the account on that date. The date columns are in ascending order from "
"left to right."
msgstr ""
"Za svaki datum u periodu prognoze, kolona prikazuje pretpostavljeni bilans "
"računa za taj datum. Kolone datuma su u rastućem poretku sa lijeve na desnu "
"stranu."

